hadiths[82]{hadithnumber,text}:
2533,"Hazrat abu-Umama Asad bin Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) ney (baaghi) logon ko jhank kar dekha to aap ney suna ke wo (Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko) qatl karney ki baaten kar rahey hain, chunanche Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : wo mujhey qatl karney key ehad o paiman kar rahey hain. ( aakhir) wo mujhey kyon qatl karna chahtey hain? mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : teen mein sey kisi eik wajeh key baghair musalman aadmi ka khoon karna jayez nahin. (eik) wo shakhs jisney shaadi shuda ho kar zina ka irtikab kya to usey rajm kya jaeyga. (doosra) wo shakhs jisney qisaas key ilawa kisi ko qatl kya, aur (teesra) wo shakhs jo Islam laney key baad murtad ho gaya. Allah ki qasam! mainey na jahiliyat mein zina kya tha, na Islam laney key baad kya hai. aur mainey kisi musalman fard ko qatl nahin kya. aur Islam laney key baad murtad bhi nahin huwa."
2534,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman aadmi is baat ki gawahi deta hai ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, aur main (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ka Rasool hun, usey qatl karna halal nahin, siwaye teen afrad key : jaan key badley mein jaan, shaadi-shuda zaani aur apney Deen ko chhod kar (musalmanon ki) jamaat sey alag ho janey wala."
2535,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apna Deen badal daley usey qatl kar do."
2536,"Hazrat Behaz bin Hakim (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Hakim bin Muawiya (Rahimahullah)) sey aur wo unkey dada (Hazrat Muawiya bin Heda qushairi (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala us mushrik ka koi amal qubul nahin karta jo Islam laney key baad mushrik ho jaey yahan tak key wo mushrikon ko chhod kar musalmanon sey aa miley ."
2537,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki muqarrar karda hadon mein sey eik had jari karna Allah azz-w-jall ki zamin mein chaalis raaton ki barish sey behtar hai."
2538,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zamin main eik (mujrim ko) had lagana zamin walon key liye chaalis din barish barasney sey behtar hai."
2539,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Quran Majeed ki eik bhi aayat ka inkar kya to usey qatl karna halal ho gaya . aur jisney kaha : akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin, aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain to (us iqrar key baad) kisi ko is par (qatl karney ya maal chheenney ka) ikhtiyar nahin, siwaye uskey ke wo kisi had waley jurm ka irtikab karey to wo had is par jari ki jaeygi."
2540,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki haden qarib waley par bhi nafiz karo aur door waley par bhi. tumhen Allah (key ehkam ki taameel) key barey mein kisi malamat karney waley ki malamat ( un par amal karney sey) rukawat na baney ."
2541,"Hazrat Atiya Qarzi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : banu Qureza ( ki saza) key din hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiye gaey to jis key (zere-naaf) baal ug aaye they usey qatl kar diya gaya aur jis key baal nahin ugey they, usey chhod diya gaya . main un afrad mein sey tha jinkey baal nahin ugey they to mujhey bhi chhod diya gaya ."
2542,"Hazrat Atiya Qarzi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney (mazkoora baala waqia bayan kartey huye) farmaya : ye main tumharey darmiyan mojud hun."
2543,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jange uhad key moqey par mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir kiya gaya to meri umr chaudah saal thi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey (jang mein shareek honey ki) ijazat na di. aur ghazwae-khandaq key moqey par, jab main pandarah saal ka tha, mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya to aap ney mujhey (jang mein shareek honey ki) ijazat dey di. Hazrat Nafey (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : mainey Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) key daure-khilaafat mein unhen ye hadees sunai to unhoney farmaya : ye (Umar) bachchey aur badey key darmiyan had faasil (rukaawat) hai."
2544,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi musalman ki parda poshi kerega to Allah Taala duniya aur aakhirat mein uska parda rakhega."
2545,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jahan tak had laganey sey bachao ki gunjaaish miley, had rafa' (door) karo."
2546,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney musalman bhai ka nangapan chhupaeyga to Allah Taala qiyamat key din uska nangapan chupaeyga. aur jo shakhs apney musalman bhai ka parda faash kerega to Allah Taala uska parda faash kerega yahan tak key usey uskey ghar key andar ruswa kar dega."
2547,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Quraish banu Makhzoom ki us khatoon key mamley mein bahut fikr mand huye jisney chori ki thi. unhoney kaha : uskey barey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey kon arz kar sakta hai? (aakhir) unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key piyarey Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) key siwa aur kon ye jur'at kar sakta hai? chunanche Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey baat ki to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya to Allah ki eik had key barey mein sifarish karta hai? phir aap uthey aur khutba irshad farmaya , (khutbey mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logo ! tum sey pehley log isi wajeh sey tabah huye ke un mein jab koi moazziz (ameer) aadmi chori karta to usey chhod detey they aur jab koi kamzor (gharib) aadmi chori karta to usey had laga detey. qism hai Allah ki ! agar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima (Raziallahu anha) bhi chori karti to main uska bhi haath kaat deta. Raavi hadees Muhammad bin Rumeh ney kaha : mainey Imam Les bin Saad (Rahimahullah) ko farmatey huye suna, wo bayan kar rahey they : Allah Taala ney unhen (Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko) chori (jaisi naazebaa harkat) sey mehfooz farmaya tha. aur har musalman ko yehi kehna chahiye (ke Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) sey is qism ki ghalati ka hona mumkin nahin lekin qanoon aa'laa aur adnaa sab key liye barabar hai)."
2548,"Hazrat Masood ibn Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab us aurat ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghar sey kambal churaa liya to hum us mamley mein bahut fikr mand huye. wo Quraish ki eik aurat thi. hum baat karney key liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur hamney kaha : hum uskey jurmaane key tor par chaalis oqiye (chaandi) dey dengey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uskey liye yehi behtar hai ke usey (saza dey kar gunah sey) paak kar diya jaey. hamney jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki naram guftgu suni to hum Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaey aur kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey baat karo. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jab ye soorate-haal dekhi to khutba deney khadey ho gaey aur farmaya : tum Allah ki eik had (key laagu hone ko rokney) key liye israr kyon kar rahey ho jo Allah ki eik bandi par aa padi hai? qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! agar Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti bhi wo ghalati karti jo us aurat ney ki hai to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uska bhi haath kaat deta."
2549,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira, Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid aur Hazrat Shabal Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke eik aadmi khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : main aap ko Allah ki qism dey kar kehta hun ke hamara faisla Allah key qanoon key mutabiq kijiye. uska mukhalif (doosra aadmi) ziyada samajh daar tha usney kaha : (ji haan) hamara faisla Allah ki kitab key mutabiq kar dijiye aur mujhey baat karney ki ijazat dijiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaho. usney kaha : mera beta is shakhs key yahan naukar tha, usney iski biwi sey bad-kari kar li. mainey sau bakriyan aur eik ghulam uska fidya dey diya. phir mainey ehle-ilm mein sey mutaaddid (bahut se) afrad (logo) sey (masla) puchha to mujhey bataya gaya ke merey betey ki saza sau kodey aur eik saal ki jala-watni hai, aur iski biwi ki saza rajm hai. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! main tumharey darmiyan Allah ki Kitab key mutabiq hi faisla karunga. sau bakriyan aur ghulam tum wapis ley lo. aur terey betey ki saza sau kodey aur eik saal ki jala-watni hai, aur (doosrey Sahaba sey farmaya : ) Unais ! is shakhs ki aurat key paas jao, agar wo (apney jurm ka) aetraaf kar ley to usey sangsaar kar dena. (Imam Ibne-Maja key ustaad) Hazrat Hisham bin Ammar ney farmaya : Hazrat Unais (Raziallahu anhu) us aurat key paas gaey (aur us sey poochha) to usney aetraaf kar liya, chunanche unhoney usey sangsaar kar diya."
2550,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujh sey (Allah ka hukm) hasil kar lo. mujh sey (Allah ka hukm) hasil kar lo. Allah Taala ney unkey liye eik raasta (aur qanoon) muqarrar kar diya hai. kunwaarey ladkey aur kanwari ladki ki saza sau kodey maarna aur eik saal key liye jala-watan karna hai. aur shaadi shuda mard aur shaadi shuda aurat ki saza sau kodey maarna aur sangsaar karna hai."
2551,"Hazrat Habib bin Salim (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) ki khidmat main eik mard pesh kiya gaya jisney apni biwi ki londi sey mubashrat (ham bistari) ki thi. Hazrat Noman (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main uskey barey mein wohi faisla karunga jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla hai. phir farmaya : agar aurat ney mard ko londi sey mubashrat (ham bistari) ki ijazat di thi to main is (mard) ko sau kodey lagaaunga. aur agar usney ijazat nahin di thi to main isey sangsaar karwa dunga."
2552,Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik mard pesh kiya gaya jisney apni biwi ki londi sey mubashrat (ham bistari) ki thi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey had nahin lagai.
2553,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey khatra hai ke logon par kuchh taweel arsa guzarney par koi shakhs ye bhi kehney lagega : mujhey Allah ki Kitab (Quran majeed) mein rajm ka zikr nahin milta. is tarah wo log Allah ka eik fariza tarak karney ki wajeh sey gumrah ho jaeyngey. suno ! rajm haq hai jabke mard shaadi shuda ho aur gawahi sabit ho jaey, ya hamal ya aetraaf mojud ho. mainey ye aayat padhi hai : (الشَّيْخُ وَالشَّيْخَةُ إِذَا زَنَيَا فَارْجُمُوهُمَا الْبَتَّةَ), ''badi umr ka mard aur badi umr ki aurat jab bad kaari karen to unhen zarur rajm kar do."" Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (is jurm ka irtikab karney walon ko) rajm ki saza di thi aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baad hamney bhi rajm ki saza di."
2554,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Maaiz bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : mainey zina kiya hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey munh pher liya. usney phir kaha : mainey zina kiya hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney munh dusri taraf kar liya. usney phir (teesri baar) kaha : mainey zina kiya hai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney munh dusri taraf pher liya. usney phir (chauthi baar) kaha : mainey zina kiya hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us sey munh phertey rahey yahan tak key usney chaar baar iqrar kar liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey rajm kiye janey ka hukm dey diya, chunanche jab isey patthar lagey to wo peeth pher kar bhaagaa. usey eik aadmi mila jis key haath mein oont key jabde ki haddi thi. usney wohi maar di jis sey wo gir gaya (aur jaan dey di). Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein patthar lagney par uskey bhagney ka zikr kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : tum ney usey chhod kyon na diya?"
2555,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik khatoon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar zina ka iqrar kiya, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey uskey kapdey achchhi tarah baandh diye gaey, phir aap ney isey sangsaar kiya, phir uski namaze-janaza ada ki."
2556,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do Yahudi afrad (eik mard aur eik aurat) ko rajm kiya. rajm karney walon mein main bhi shamil tha. mainey us (yahudi) ko dekha ke wo us (aurat) ko pattharon sey bachaney ki koshish kar raha tha.
2557,Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik Yahudi mard aur eik Yahudi aurat ko sangsaar kiya.
2558,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik Yahudi key paas sey guzrey jis ka munh kaalaa kiya gaya tha aur usey kodey maarey gaey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen bulaya aur farmaya : kya tumhen apni kitab mein zaani ki yehi saza milti hai? unhoney kaha : haan. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey ulama mein sey eik aadmi ko bulaya aur farmaya : main tujhey us Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun jisney Musa (Alaihissalam) par Torat nazil ki ! kya tum zaani ki yehi saza (Toraat mein) paatey ho? usney kaha : nahin. aur agar aap ney mujhey qism na di hoti to main aap ko (sahih baat) na batata. hamari kitab mein zaani ki saza rajm hi hai lekin hamarey ashraaf mein rajm (wala jurm) bahut ziyada honey laga to (hum yun karney lagey ke) jab hum kisi moazziz ko (is jurm ka irtikab kartey huye) pakad letey to usey (saza diye baghair) chhod detey, aur jab kisi kamzor ko pakad letey to usey had laga detey. (isliye) hamney (aapas mein) kaha : aao hum kisi aisi saza par ittifaq kar lein jo moazziz aur kamzor (dono qism key mujrimon) ko dey saken, chunanche hamney rajm ki bajaey munh kaalaa karney aur kodey maarney par ittifaq kar liya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! sab sey pehley main terey hukm ko zinda karta hun jabke unhoney is ko murda kar diya hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey is mujrim ko sangsaar kar diya gaya."
2559,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar main kisi ko gawahi qaaim huye baghair rajm karta to falan aurat ko zarur rajm kar deta. uski baat cheet, chaal dhaal aur uskey paas aaney janey walon ki wajeh sey wo ba-zahir mashkook nazar aati hai."
2560,"Hazrat Qasim (Rahimahullah) (bin Muhammad bin Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney liaan karney waley mard aur aurat ka zikr kiya to ibne Shaddad ney kaha : kya ye wohi aurat thi jis key barey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : agar main kisi ko baghair gawahi key sangsaar karta to us aurat ko sangsaar karta? Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : (nahin) wo to elaaniya fohsh (gandi) harkaat karti thi."
2561,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey tum Hazrat Loot (Alaihissalam) ki qom wala kaam kartey dekho to karne wale aur karwane wale dono ko qatl kar do."
2562,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us shakhs key barey mein, jo Hazrat Loot (Alaihissalam) ki (bad kaar) qom wali harkat karta hai, farmaya : ooper waley aur nichey waley ko sangsaar kar do. un dono ko sangsaar kar do."
2563,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey apni ummat par jin gunahon (mein mubtala honey) ka khatra hai, un mein sey sab sey ziyada khatra qome Loot key amal (mein mubtala honey) ka hai."
2564,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs mehram aurat sey bad kaari karey to usey qatl kar do. aur jo shakhs kisi janwer sey bad-kaari karey to usey bhi qatl kar do, aur us janwer ko bhi halak kar do."
2565,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera , Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid aur Hazrat Shabal Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke eik aadmi ney aap sey us londi key barey mein sawal kiya jo shaadi sey pehley zina kar ley. to aap ney farmaya : usey kodey lagao, phir agar (dobara) zina karey to usey kodey lagao. phir teesri ya chauthi baar farmaya : phir usey farokht kar do, chahey baalon ki eik rassi key iwaz farokht ho."
2566,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab londi zina karey to usey kodey lagao. agar phir zina karey to kodey lagao. agar phir zina karey to kodey lagao. agar phir zina karey to kodey lagao, phir usey bech dalo agar-che rassi key iwaz ho. (Raavi ney kaha : )  (zafeer) sey murad rassi hai."
2567,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab meri bara-at (ilzaam se bari hone wali aayat) nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney member par khadey ho kar uska zikr farmaya aur Quran (ki mutalliqa aayaat) ki tilawat farmaai. jab member sey utrey to do mardon aur eik aurat ko (had laganey ka) hukm jari farmaya, chunanche unhen had lagai gaee."
2568,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi mard doosrey ko kahey : aey mukhannas ! (aey heejdey !) to usey bees kodey maaro. aur jab koi mard doosrey mard ko kahey : aey looti ! to usey bees kodey maaro."
2569,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main jis par had lagaaun, uski diyat nahin dunga siwaye sharab peeney waley key kyonkey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey liye koi khas saza muqarrar nahin ki. ye to hum logon ney khud muqarrar kar li hai."
2570,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sharab peene key jurm mein jooton aur chhadiyon sey saza detey they."
2571,Hazrat Hizeen bin Munzir (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Waleed bin Aqba key khilaf (sharab peene ki) gawahi milney par jab unhen Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key samney hazir kiya gaya to unhoney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : apney chacha key betey par had qaaim karo. Hazrat Ali ney unhen kodey maarey aur farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chaalis kodey maarey they aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi chaalis kodey maarey they aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney assi kodey maarey. ye sab sazaaen sunnat hain.
2572,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar koi nasha karey to usey kodey lagao. agar dobara (ye jurm) karey to usey kodey lagao. agar phir (ye jurm) karey to usey kodey lagao. phir chauthi baar farmaya : agar phir (ye jurm)  karey to usey qatl kar do."
2573,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar log sharab pi lein to unhen kodey maaro. phir agar (dobara) piyen to unhen kodey maaro. agar phir (teesri baar) piyen to unhen kodey maaro. agar phir (chauthi baar) piyen to unhen qatl kar do."
2574,"Hazrat Saeed bin Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamarey mahalley main eik kamzor apahaj rehta tha. (eik din) log ye dekh kar hairaan reh gaey ke wo ghar ki eik laundi sey burey kaam mein mashghool hai. Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ney uska maamla Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey sau kodey maaro. arz kiya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! wo to bahut kamzor hai. agar hamney usey sau kodey maarey to wo mar jaeyga. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khajoor ka eik khosha lo, (jis par sey khajuren utaar li gaee hon aur tinkey baqi hon) jis mein so tinkey hon. usey uski eik zarab laga do. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney Sufiyan bin Wakee key wastey sey bhi mazkura riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
2575,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney hamarey khilaf hathiyar uthaya wo hum mein sey nahin."
2576,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney hum par hathiyar uthaya wo hum mein sey nahin."
2577,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Abdullah bin Qais Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney hum par (hamla karney key liye) hathiyar nikala wo hum mein sey nahin."
2578,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein qabila Uraina key kuchh log Madina aaye. unhen Madina Munawra ki  hawa aur paani muwaafiq na aai to aap ney farmaya : agar tum hamarey oonton (key rewad) mein chaley jao aur unka doodh aur peshab piyo (to behtar ho jaogey). unhoney aisey hi kiya. phir (jab wo sehat yaab ho gaey to) wo Islam chhod kar murtad ho gaey, aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key charwahey ko shaheed kar diya. aur aap key oont haank kar ley gaey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un ki giraftaari key liye chand afrad bhejey, chunanche unhen (giraftar kar key) laya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey haath paon kaat diye aur garm salaaiyon sey un ki aankhen phod den. aur unhen Harra mein chhod diya yahan tak key wo mar gaey."
2579,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke kuchh logon ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki doodh wali oontniyaan loot lein to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey haath paon kaat diye, aur lohey ki garm salaaiyon sey un ki aankhen phod den."
2580,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid bin Amr bin Nafeel (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney maal ko (chor ya daaku sey) bachaney key liye (uska muqabla kartey huye) qatl ho gaya, wo shaheed hai."
2581,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis key maal key paas koi aaye aur (usey leney ki koshish karey , jab wo bachana chahey to) us sey jang ki jaey, tab wo ( hamla aawar sey) ladey aur qatl ho jaey to wo shaheed hai."
2582,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis sey zulm key tor par uska maal talab kya jaey, wo qatl ho jaey to wo shaheed hai."
2583,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala lanat farmaaey us chor par jo anda churata hai to (bil-aakhir) uska haath kaat diya jata hai aur rassi churata hai to uska haath kaat diya jata hai."
2584,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik dhaal (ki chori) ki wajeh sey (chor ka) haath kaata. us (dhaal) ki qeemat teen dirham thi.
2585,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haath sirf chothai Dinar ya us sey ziyada (ki chori) ki wajeh sey kaata jaeyga.
2586,"Hazrat Aamir bin Saad (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chor ka haath dhaal ki qeemat ( key barabar chori karney key jurm) mein kaata jaeyga."
2587,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mehriz (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey (chor key) galey mein haath latkaaney key barey mein sawal kya to unhoney farmaya : ye sunnat hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ka haath kaata, phir wo uski gardan mein latka diya."
2588,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Solba Ansari (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Solba bin Amr bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat Amr bin Samra bin Habib bin Abd Shams (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey banu falan ka eik oont chori kya hai. mujhey (saza dey kar gunah sey) pak kar dijiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un logon ko pegham bheja (aur daryaft kya) unhoney kaha : hamara eik oont gum ho gaya hai, chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uski baabat hukm diya to uska haath kaat diya gaya. Hazrat Solba (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jab uska haath ( kat kar) gira to main usey dekh raha tha, jabke (us waqt) wo (apney haath ko mukhatib kar key) keh raha tha : Allah ka shukr hai jisney mujhey tujh sey pak kar diya. (aey haath !) to chahta tha ke merey jism ko jahannam mein ley jaey ."
2589,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab ghulam chori karey to usey bech dalo , chahey nisf oqiye key iwaz ( farokht ho)."
2590,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke khums key ghulamon mein sey eik ghulam ney khums key maal mein sey kuch chura liya . usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya gaya to aap ney uska haath na kaata. aur farmaya : Allah key maal (ghulam) ney Allah ka maal chori kya hai.
2591,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khayanat karney waley ka haath kaata jaey, na chheenney waley ka aur na uchakney waley ka."
2592,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna : uchakney waley ki saza haath kaatna nahin hai."
2593,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal churaney ya khajoor ka gooda churaney par haath nahin kaata jaeyga."
2594,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal churaney ya khajoor ka gooda churaney par haath nahin kaata jaeyga."
2595,Hazrat Abdullah bin Safwan (Raziallahu anhuma) apney walid (Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke wo masjid mein so rahey they aur apni chadar sar key nichey rakhi hui thi . kisi ney unkey sar key nichey sey chadar nikal li . wo chor ko pakad kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley gaey . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uska haath kaatney ka hukm dey diya . Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mera irada ye nahin tha (ke uska haath katwa dun) meri chadar is par sadqa hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum ney isey merey paas laney sey pehley kyon (ye sadqa) na kya ?
2596,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke qabila muzena key eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey phalon ( ki chori) key barey mein daryaft kya to aap ney farmaya : jo phal khoshon mein sey (nikal kar) utha kar ley jaya jaey to (uska jurmaana) uski qeemat aur uskey sath itni hi raqam mazeed (jurmana wasul kya jaeyga.) aur jo sikhaaney key maidan sey (ley jaya gaya) ho to wo agar dhaal ki qeemat tak pahunchta ho to uski saza mein haath kaata jaeyga. agar usney khaya hai aur sath nahin ley gaya to usey koi saza nahin. usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! jo bakri (raat ko) baadey sey bahar reh jaey (aur usey koi chura ley to?) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uski qeemat aur uskey sath itni hi raqam mazeed aur (jismani) saza bhi . aur jo ( bakri ) baadey mein sey churaai jaey to uski saza haath kaatna hai jabke dhaal ki qeemat tak pahunchti ho.
2597,"Hazrat Abu-Umaiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik chor pesh kya gaya. usney jurm qabool kar liya jabke uskey paas saman na mila. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey khayal main tu ney chori nahin ki. usney kaha : kyon nahin (balke ki hai.) phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey khayal main tu ney chori nahin ki. usney kaha : kyon nahin (balke ki hai.) chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey uska haath kaat diya gaya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ke! ( اَسْتَغْفِرُاللّهَ وَاَتُوْبُ إِلَيْهِ ) main Allah sey bakhshish talab karta hun aur uskey huzur tauba karta hun . usney kaha : ( استغفرالله واتوب اليه ) , mein Allah sey bakhshish talab karta hun aur uskey huzur tauba karta hun . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do baar farmaya : aey Allah ! uski tauba qubul farma ."
2598,"Abdul-jabbar bin Wayl ney apney walid (Hazrat Wayl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat ki hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney main eik aurat sey zabardasti badkari ka irtikab kya gaya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey had sey bari kar diya, aur us shakhs par had jari ki jisney us sey badkaari ki thi. Sahabi ney ye zikr nahin kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us aurat ko mehar dlwaya tha (ya nahin.)"
2599,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : masjidon mein haden na lagai jaeyn."
2600,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib (Rahimahullah) ney apney walid sey, aur unhoney apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat kya hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney masjidon mein had laganey sey mana farmaya."
2601,"Hazrat Abu-Barda bin Niyar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : Allah ki muqarrar karda hadon mein sey kisi had key ilawa kisi (mujrim) ko das sey ziyada kodey na maarey jaeyn."
2602,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : das kodon sey ziyada saza na lagao."
2603,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jis shakhs sey had key qabil jurm sarzad ho jaey, phir usey jaldi (duniya hi mein) saza mil jaey to ye uska kaffara bin jati hai. warna (agar wo dunyawi saza sey bach jaey to) uska maamla Allah key supurd hai."
2604,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis sey duniya mein koi gunah sar zad ho jaey, phir usey (duniya mein) uski saza mil jaey to Allah Taala key insaf sey door hai ke apney bandey ko dobara us (gunah) ki saza dey. aur jisney duniya mein koi gunah kiya, phir Allah ney uska parda rakh liya to Allah key karam sey door hai ke jis gunah ko maaf kar diya hai, dobara uski saza dey."
2605,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Saad bin Ubada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar koi aadmi apni biwi key paas kisi (ajnabi) mard ko paey to kya usey qatl kar dey? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin. Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kyon nahin? qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq (aur sachchey deen) sey sarfaraaz farmaya. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : suno ! tumhara sardar kya kehta hai.
2606,"Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : jab hudood ki aayat nazil hui to Hazrat Abu-Saabit Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) jo bahut ghairat mand aadmi they un sey kisi ney kaha : agar aap apni biwi key paas kisi mard ko paeyn to kya kerengey? unhoney kaha : main to dono ko talwaar maar (kar qatl kar) dunga. kya main intizar karun ke chaar gawah ley kar aaun? us waqt to wo (mujrim) apna kaam kar key ja chuka hoga. aur agar main kahun ke mainey aisa aisa maamla dekha hai to tum mujhey (bohtan ki) had lagaogey, aur aainda kabhi meri gawahi qubul nahin karogey. ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney zikr ki gaee to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : talwaar ki gawahi kafi hai.  phir farmaya : nahin, mujhey dar hai ke nashey waley aur ghairat-mand pai-dar-pai qatl karney lagengey. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey Imam abu-Zara'a sey suna , wo keh rahey they : ye Ali bin Muhammad Tanaafusi ki hadees hai, aur mujh sey iska kuchh hissa zaya ho gaya hai."
2607,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey mamu (Hazrat Haris bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) merey paas sey guzrey, unhen Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik jhandaa dey kar (kisi muhim par) rawana farmaya tha. mainey kaha : aap kahan ja rahey hain? unhoney kaha : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik shakhs ki taraf (usey saza deney key liye) rawana farmaya hai, usney baap key marney key baad uski biwi (apni soteli walida) sey nikah kar liya hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey hukm diya hai ke uski gardan uda dun."
2608,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Qurra (Rahimahullah) ney apney walid Hazrat Qurra bin Ayas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik shakhs ki taraf bheja jisney apney walid ki biwi sey nikah kar liya tha (aur mujhey hukm diya) ke main usey qatl kar dun aur uska maal zabt kar lun."
2609,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney baap key siwa kisi aur ki taraf nisbat kerey. aur jo (ghulam ya londi) apney Mola (azad karney waley) key ilawa kisi aur ko apna Mola qarar dey, is par Allah ki, farishton ki aur tamam logon ki lanat hai."
2610,"Hazrat Saad aur Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, un dono mein sey har eik ney farmaya : merey kanon ney Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad Mubarak suna aur merey dil ney isey yad rakha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : jo shakhs jaan boojh kar apney baap key siwa kisi doosrey ki taraf apni nisbat karta hai, is par jannat haram hai."
2611,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney walid key siwa kisi aur ki taraf nisbat karta hai to wo jannat ki khushbu nahin paeyga, halanke uski khushbu paanch so saal key fasley sey mehsus hoti hai."
2612,"Hazrat Ash-as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main qabila kanda key wafad mein shamil ho kar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa . wafad key log mujhey apna afzal fard samajhtey they. mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aap log hum mein sey) hamarey qabiley mein sey) nahin ? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum Nazar bin Kanana ki aulad hain. hum apni maa ko tohmat nahin lagatey aur apney baap sey laa-taalluq nahin hotey. Hazrat Ash-as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey they : agar merey paas koi aisa aadmi laya jaey jo Quraish key kisi aadmi ko Nazar bin Kanana ki aulad sey khaarij qarar dey to main usey (bohtan ki) had lagaaunga."
2613,"Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke (eik heejda) Umra bin Qurra aa gaya . usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ney meri qismat mein bad bakhti likh di (ke main heejdaa hun .) merey rizq ka zaria sirf haath sey daf bajana hai to aap mujhey aisey gaaney ki ijazat dey dijiye jis mein be-hayai ki baaten na hon. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main tujhey ijazat nahin deta . na teri izzat karta hun . na (teri darkhaast qubul kar key) teri aankhen thandi karta hun . Allah key dushman ! to jhoot boltaa hai. Allah ney tujhey pak aur halal rizq diya lekin tu ney Allah key halal kiye huye ko chhod kar uska haram kya huwa rizq pasand kya. agar mainey pehley bhi tujhey (us kaam sey) mana kya hota to ( aaj) mein tujhey sakht saza deta . merey paas sey chala ja aur Allah key aagey tauba kar . sun ley ! agar tu ney ye kaam merey mana karney key baad kya hota to main teri sakht pitaai karta aur tera sar moond kar teri shakal bigaad deta aur tujhey terey khandan sey nikal kar jala watan kar deta aur tera maal Madiney key jawaanon ko loot leney ki ijazat dey deta . Amr itna zaleel aur ruswa ho kar gaya ke uski haalat Allah hi janta hai. jab wo uth gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye nafarman log hain. un mein sey jo koi tauba kiye baghair mar jaeyga to Allah azz-w-jall usey qiyamat ko usi haalat mein uthaeyga jaisey ke wo duniya mein tha, yani mukhannas aur nanga. uskey paas logon sey jism chhipaaney key liye eik cheethda bhi nahin hoga . jab bhi (chalney key liye) uthega be hosh har kar gir padega ."
2614,ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey yahan tashrif laye to suna ke eik mukhannas Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Umaiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey keh raha tha : agar kal Allah Taala ney Taaif mein Fateh nasib farma di to main tujhey eik aurat dikhaunga jo aati hai to jism mein chaar bal padtey hain aur jati hai to aath bal padtey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : unhen apney gharon sey nikal diya karo.
